-Victor, lllona.
-Bill, Alice.

33
00:02:46,731 --> 00:02:49,165
-Merry Christmas.
-Thank you for coming.

34
00:02:49,532 --> 00:02:53,810
-Thanks so much for coming.
-We wouldn't miss it for the world.

35
00:02:54,012 --> 00:02:56,970
Alice, look at you.
God, you' re absolutely stunning!

36
00:02:57,172 --> 00:02:59,002
l don't say that to all the women.
