l desperately need
to go to the bathroom.

57
00:04:40,172 --> 00:04:44,005
You go and say hello, and l'll
meet you where? At the bar?

58
00:04:44,492 --> 00:04:45,526
Good.

59
00:04:55,531 --> 00:04:56,930
Nightingale.

60
00:04:57,732 --> 00:04:58,846
Nick Nightingale!

61
