and she had a bad reaction.

162
00:12:57,371 --> 00:12:58,486
What did she take?

163
00:12:59,572 --> 00:13:02,802
A speedball or a snowball
or whatever the hell they call it.

164
00:13:03,011 --> 00:13:04,764
lt's heroin and coke.

165
00:13:07,611 --> 00:13:09,523
Heroin and coke?

166
00:13:11,932 --> 00:13:13,206
Anything else?

167
00:13:14,812 --> 00:13:17,928
We had a couple of drinks,
some champagne. That was it.

168
00:13:18,371 --> 00:13:20,009
How long has she been like this?

169
00:13:20,451 --> 00:13:23,524
Maybe five minutes, six minutes,
something like that.

170
00:13:23,731 --> 00:13:24,801
