Mandy.

172
00:13:36,251 --> 00:13:38,048
Can you hear me, Mandy?

173
00:13:39,451 --> 00:13:42,807
Can you hear me?
Move your head if you can hear me.

174
00:13:44,251 --> 00:13:47,210
Move your head if you can
hear me, Mandy. There you go.

175
00:13:47,412 --> 00:13:48,924
You can hear me.

176
00:13:49,131 --> 00:13:53,171
Can you open your eyes for me?
Mandy, can you do that?

177
00:13:53,851 --> 00:13:57,048
Let me see you open your eyes.
There you go, come on.

178
00:13:57,251 --> 00:14:00,129
Come on, look at me. Look at me.

179
00:14:00,652 --> 00:14:03,041
Look at me. Look at me.

180
00:14:03,851 --> 00:14:06,809
Look at me. Look at me, Mandy.

181
00:14:08,451 --> 00:14:09,361
Good.

182
00:14:10,812 --> 00:14:12,130
Good.

183
00:14:13,971 --> 00:14:17,168
l love Victor's art collection,
don't you?

184
00:14:20,932 --> 00:14:22,729
lt's wonderful.

185
00:14:24,211 --> 00:14:27,044
Have you ever seen
his sculpture gallery?

186
00:14:31,172 --> 00:14:32,809
l haven't.

187
00:14:33,572 --> 00:14:38,168
He has a wonderful collection
of Renaissance bronzes.

188
00:14:40,292 --> 00:14:42,327
Do you like the period?

189
00:14:45,412 --> 00:14:47,004
l do.

190
00:14:47,611 --> 00:14:49,682
l adore it.

191
00:14:51,692 --> 00:14:54,047
The sculpture gallery is upstairs.

192
00:14:55,451 --> 00:14:57,363
Would you like to see it?

193
00:15:00,331 --> 00:15:02,049
l can show it to you.

194
00:15:05,491 --> 00:15:07,322
We won't be gone long.

195
00:15:14,451 --> 00:15:16,169
Maybe. . .

196
00:15:18,731 --> 00:15:21,724
. . .not just. . .

197
00:15:22,851 --> 00:15:24,205
. . .now.

198
00:15:41,532 --> 00:15:45,605
That was really one hell
of a scare you gave us, kiddo.

199
00:15:47,132 --> 00:15:48,405
Sorry.

200
00:15:57,092 --> 00:15:59,083
How are you feeling now, Mandy?

201
00:16:01,051 --> 00:16:02,121
Better.

202
00:16:11,372 --> 00:16:15,650
You are a very, very lucky girl.

203
00:16:16,731 --> 00:16:18,050
You know that?

204
00:16:20,211 --> 00:16:21,724
l know.

205
00:16:22,731 --> 00:16:24,961
You' re gonna be okay this time.

206
00:16:26,172 --> 00:16:29,288
But you can't keep doing this.

207
00:16:30,011 --> 00:16:31,444
You understand?

208
00:16:35,692 --> 00:16:39,401
